title: 820-00165 Not booting completely. No power on pins 5 and 6 of SPI ROM
message: I get a little pulse after applying power but then it goes to 0V. This board was working and then stopped booting. I know this was a liquid spill, but I don't see any signs of damage. Any idea what would cause those two pins to lose power? Area around U6100 looks good. I've checked continuity and resistors around and leading into the area.
